// ctrl.panic/E3: the first panic wins. The body panics with "primary", then an
// ensure panics with "secondary" during unwind — that one is contained and
// reported to stderr as a secondary panic, while the remaining ensure ("cleanup",
// E2) still runs. The task's panic stays "primary"; exit 101 (P4).
func main() {
    ensure println("cleanup")
    ensure panic("secondary")
    panic("primary")
}
